1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 58 =

20
00:01:45,660 --> 00:01:46,420
Father!

21
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:51,340
I’m here.

22
00:01:57,580 --> 00:01:58,500
Huirou,

23
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:03,660
there you are.

24
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:05,980
I...

25
00:02:07,420 --> 00:02:09,420
I didn’t punish Cao Ping.

26
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:13,260
I never intended to destroy him.

27
00:02:15,620 --> 00:02:16,460
It’s just...

28
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:19,780
that a man like him

29
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:24,260
might not love you enough.

30
00:02:27,540 --> 00:02:29,500
I didn’t mean what I said.

31
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:32,060
You’d never

32
00:02:33,260 --> 00:02:34,940
punish an innocent man.

33
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:40,620
I was just disappointed.

34
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:53,620
It was my fault.

35
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:56,100
I shouldn’t have hurt you.

36
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:07,820
I didn’t know you fell ill.

37
00:03:10,820 --> 00:03:11,500
I...

38
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:14,380
I missed you every day

39
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:19,940
but I feared

40
00:03:22,260 --> 00:03:23,500
that after everything I said,

41
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:26,900
you’d stop loving me

42
00:03:27,620 --> 00:03:29,020
and abandon me.

43
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:31,300
Huirou,

44
00:03:32,820 --> 00:03:34,580
I’d never abandon you.

45
00:03:44,340 --> 00:03:45,100
Father,

46
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:48,420
let’s make a deal.

47
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:51,300
From now on,

48
00:03:52,260 --> 00:03:54,420
I’ll be staying here

49
00:03:54,820 --> 00:03:55,700
with you

50
00:03:56,380 --> 00:03:57,300
to look after you.

51
00:03:58,820 --> 00:04:00,620
When flowers at the Court of Spring

52
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:02,820
and Court of Rarity bloom,

53
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:04,460
you’ll recover.

54
00:04:05,820 --> 00:04:07,740
We’ll be as good as before

55
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:11,180
and see flowers together, right?

56
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:29,620
Officer Ren,

57
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:32,420
father asks to see two ministers.

58
00:04:57,340 --> 00:04:58,620
His Majesty says...

59
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:14,620
His Majesty says

60
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:16,940
to recall Zhang Maoze back to the Capital.

61
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:20,140
His Majesty’s been unwell for long

62
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:21,300
and looks forward to seeing familiar faces.

63
00:05:22,020 --> 00:05:24,020
Maoze’s always loyal and meticulous

64
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:25,780
who was with His Majesty for decades

65
00:05:25,780 --> 00:05:26,780
without making any mistakes.

66
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:28,660
Starting from today,

67
00:05:28,860 --> 00:05:31,340
Zhang Maoze will be attending upon His Majesty.

68
00:05:40,980 --> 00:05:41,820
Zhang Maoze,

69
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:44,660
His Majesty is weak.

70
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:46,620
Do take good care of him

71
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:49,620
with your best effort.

72
00:05:50,700 --> 00:05:51,820
You can’t leave without permission.

73
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:03,100
Yes, Your Majesty.

74
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:13,820
Your Highness,

75
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:17,500
ministers wish to set up an altar
in the Hall of Celebration

76
00:06:17,940 --> 00:06:20,700
to burn incense and pray for His Majesty.

77
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:22,220
Please allow them

78
00:06:22,300 --> 00:06:24,540
to rest in the west side chamber

79
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:26,820
at night.

80
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:30,660
There’s no precedent

81
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:32,100
for ministers resting in the palace.

82
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:33,980
Precedents don’t apply

83
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:36,580
to the current circumstance.

84
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:49,300
Your Highness,

85
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:52,740
we’re taking our leave.

86
00:06:54,340 --> 00:06:55,460
His Majesty is sick.

87
00:06:58,020 --> 00:06:59,860
I’m unable

88
00:07:00,660 --> 00:07:01,580
to make decisions for him.

89
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,660
The burden is all on you.

90
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:21,020
Your Highness,

91
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:24,620
let me help you get ready for bed.

92
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:45,634
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

93
00:07:46,789 --> 00:07:49,401
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

94
00:07:49,500 --> 00:07:51,180
Who’s lonelier?

95
00:07:56,620 --> 00:07:57,700
You still have Huirou.

96
00:07:57,979 --> 00:08:02,758
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

97
00:08:02,940 --> 00:08:03,700
Who do I have?

98
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:08,160
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

99
00:08:09,262 --> 00:08:14,810
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

100
00:08:14,810 --> 00:08:19,885
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

101
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:22,860
Death.

102
00:08:23,290 --> 00:08:28,424
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

103
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:29,780
This state is yours.

104
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:34,540
You can’t run out

105
00:08:34,540 --> 00:08:39,140
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

106
00:08:39,140 --> 00:08:40,460
on your responsibility.

107
00:08:40,460 --> 00:08:45,606
♪ We only have each other in this cage♪

108
00:08:53,780 --> 00:08:55,020
Kuanfu, do you really believe

109
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:56,100
such nonsense?

110
00:08:56,540 --> 00:08:57,900
Ridiculous hogwash

111
00:08:57,900 --> 00:08:59,020
such as dogs growing horns

112
00:08:59,020 --> 00:09:00,060
is written in the proposal

113
00:09:00,060 --> 00:09:01,100
to impeach Chief Executive of Privy Council.

114
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:03,100
Allowing hearsay to be reported

115
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:04,380
is to invite more suggestions

116
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:06,420
not to cook up or spread rumors.

117
00:09:06,820 --> 00:09:08,540
As ridiculous as the statement is,

118
00:09:08,700 --> 00:09:09,420
concerns from

119
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:10,580
so many court scholars

120
00:09:10,580 --> 00:09:11,540
aren’t completely groundless.

121
00:09:11,820 --> 00:09:12,620
After all,

122
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:13,740
promoting a general

123
00:09:13,780 --> 00:09:14,660
to Chief Executive

124
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:15,780
is against the tradition.

125
00:09:15,900 --> 00:09:16,900
Court scholars?

126
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:18,700
All I see is a bunch of liars.

127
00:09:19,140 --> 00:09:20,060
Di Qing

128
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:21,580
didn’t do anything wrong.

129
00:09:22,300 --> 00:09:23,620
He’s a gallant

130
00:09:23,900 --> 00:09:24,980
and decorated war hero

131
00:09:25,180 --> 00:09:26,260
who safeguarded our national prestige.

132
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:27,580
Since Commander Cao passed away,

133
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:28,700
our nation has been yearning

134
00:09:28,700 --> 00:09:29,860
for another hero for so long.

135
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:32,540
The one who should be impeached...

136
00:09:32,940 --> 00:09:34,580
Prime Minister Fu is a good man

137
00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:36,940
but Prime Minister Wen, who once gave lantern silk

138
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:38,860
to Madam Zhang, is arguing with him.

139
00:09:39,020 --> 00:09:40,340
Prime Minister Wen must be wrong,

140
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:41,340
right?

141
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:43,980
I don’t understand

142
00:09:44,220 --> 00:09:45,060
state affairs.

143
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:47,060
Liar.

144
00:09:47,340 --> 00:09:48,580
You’ve been with father every day,

145
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:50,700
copying and reading proposals for him.

146
00:09:50,820 --> 00:09:51,700
How could you not know?

147
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:54,580
Fine. You don’t need to answer me.

148
00:09:54,860 --> 00:09:55,740
Lately,

149
00:09:55,740 --> 00:09:57,300
I’m with father all the time.

150
00:09:57,540 --> 00:09:59,580
These ministers come to see him often.

151
00:10:00,060 --> 00:10:01,700
Di Qing they mentioned

152
00:10:01,820 --> 00:10:03,380
is a war hero.

153
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:04,700
Father likes him,

154
00:10:04,900 --> 00:10:05,780
so he promoted him

155
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:07,540
but scholars who aren’t battlewise

156
00:10:07,620 --> 00:10:08,740
disapproved of his decision.

157
00:10:10,820 --> 00:10:12,180
You’re wise, princess.

158
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:14,180
You figured it all out on your own.

159
00:10:39,660 --> 00:10:41,740
Father, is it sweet?

160
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:43,860
I learned from mother

161
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:44,860
and made this myself.

162
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:48,660
You’ve done

163
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:50,180
good enough.

164
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:52,860
That doesn’t

165
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:54,420
sound like a compliment.

166
00:11:06,300 --> 00:11:07,700
You know, I’m craving for...

167
00:11:10,700 --> 00:11:11,620
For what?

168
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:13,340
I can learn to make it.

169
00:11:16,700 --> 00:11:17,700
I don’t think

170
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:20,260
you can do it well.

171
00:11:21,540 --> 00:11:22,540
Just tell me.

172
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:30,180
I want to eat dried meat

173
00:11:30,980 --> 00:11:31,820
and drink liquor Her Highness made.

174
00:11:34,340 --> 00:11:36,780
Physicians said you can’t.

175
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:39,060
I can still smell them.

176
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:40,620
No.

177
00:11:41,420 --> 00:11:43,660
She’s on a vegetarian diet and copying sutras

178
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:45,460
to pray for you.

179
00:11:45,780 --> 00:11:47,700
She won’t make liquor or roast meat for you.

180
00:11:49,260 --> 00:11:51,940
The kitchen can,

181
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:55,460
or let my mother do it.

182
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:56,780
Then...

183
00:11:59,660 --> 00:12:01,420
Then I’ll wait for her

184
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:03,700
until she finishes copying them.

185
00:12:07,100 --> 00:12:07,980
But father,

186
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:09,980
there are so many Buddhist texts.

187
00:12:10,660 --> 00:12:12,540
Even a lifetime isn’t enough

188
00:12:12,820 --> 00:12:14,140
to copy them all.

189
00:12:20,140 --> 00:12:21,100
She probably

190
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:24,260
doesn’t want to see me again

191
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:25,660
for the rest of her life.

192
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:31,100
Your Highness.

193
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:40,380
You’re really on a vegetarian diet!

194
00:12:42,980 --> 00:12:44,620
Why would I lie to you?

195
00:12:51,940 --> 00:12:53,140
I know

196
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:54,620
you never lie

197
00:12:55,980 --> 00:12:57,420
but in father’s eyes,

198
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,020
your diet

199
00:12:59,020 --> 00:13:00,620
is only an excuse

200
00:13:00,900 --> 00:13:02,420
for not making dried meat for him.

201
00:13:06,740 --> 00:13:08,300
Once he’s healthy enough

202
00:13:08,660 --> 00:13:09,660
to eat meat,

203
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:11,900
Imperial Chefs will cook it for him.

204
00:13:13,180 --> 00:13:13,980
Or,

205
00:13:14,140 --> 00:13:15,460
he can go to other concubines.

206
00:13:16,860 --> 00:13:17,900
I dare not

207
00:13:18,820 --> 00:13:19,940
make food for him.

208
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:22,140
Your Highness,

209
00:13:22,460 --> 00:13:24,300
you aren’t going to forgive father?

210
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:28,780
No wonder he said

211
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:31,100
you’d never finish copying sutras.

212
00:13:33,820 --> 00:13:34,740
That’s not too bad, though.

213
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:36,420
He also said

214
00:13:36,620 --> 00:13:38,340
if you wouldn’t cook for him,

215
00:13:38,540 --> 00:13:39,540
he’d stop

216
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:40,820
eating dried meat for the rest of his life.

217
00:13:45,540 --> 00:13:46,500
Impossible!

218
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:49,500
Although father

219
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:51,980
has upset you

220
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:53,220
and hurt you more than once,

221
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:55,700
he’s never lied to you.

222
00:13:56,940 --> 00:13:59,220
If you’re going to be a vegan,

223
00:13:59,420 --> 00:14:00,500
so will he.

224
00:14:00,700 --> 00:14:01,340
Good.

225
00:14:02,540 --> 00:14:03,300
Eating vegetables

226
00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:05,300
is good for his health.

227
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:09,260
He loves meat and liquor.

228
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:16,660
Others assume your father is gentle,

229
00:14:16,660 --> 00:14:17,620
tender and abstemious.

230
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:19,500
In fact...

231
00:14:23,140 --> 00:14:27,180
He fancies goodies and girls.

232
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:31,580
Your Highness, do you know what you’re saying?

233
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:42,020
You know,

234
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:45,540
he loves eating spicy, fried food and seafood

235
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:48,340
but he knows that’s wrong

236
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:50,580
not because

237
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:53,100
it’s bad for his health

238
00:14:54,540 --> 00:14:56,780
but because it’s against

239
00:14:57,100 --> 00:14:57,900
the principles.

240
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:01,100
That an emperor shouldn’t indulge himself

241
00:15:01,220 --> 00:15:02,620
in luxurious foods.

242
00:15:04,180 --> 00:15:06,460
So he’s restraining

243
00:15:06,460 --> 00:15:08,060
all his excessive desires

244
00:15:08,900 --> 00:15:10,620
to be a perfect role model.

245
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:17,860
Sometimes,

246
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:21,140
seeing him

247
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:23,180
sipping the liquor enjoyably

248
00:15:24,100 --> 00:15:26,140
and nibbling

249
00:15:27,020 --> 00:15:29,500
at the dried meat

250
00:15:31,020 --> 00:15:32,460
with smiles on his face,

251
00:15:38,740 --> 00:15:40,020
I find him adorable

252
00:15:43,460 --> 00:15:44,700
yet pitiful.

253
00:15:48,220 --> 00:15:48,980
Your Highness,

254
00:15:50,180 --> 00:15:51,900
please forgive him one more time.

255
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:55,260
Look at me.

256
00:15:56,140 --> 00:15:56,860
I lashed out at father

257
00:15:56,860 --> 00:15:58,140
and hurt him so much

258
00:15:58,700 --> 00:15:59,860
that he even spat blood out.

259
00:16:01,260 --> 00:16:02,300
I regretted it a ton

260
00:16:02,820 --> 00:16:04,100
and wished I could die for him

261
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:05,500
or relive the past.

262
00:16:07,060 --> 00:16:08,580
Thankfully, he forgave me.

263
00:16:10,660 --> 00:16:11,780
Your Highness,

264
00:16:12,340 --> 00:16:14,260
stop your diet,

265
00:16:14,660 --> 00:16:15,420
please?

266
00:16:17,460 --> 00:16:18,300
A while ago,

267
00:16:18,620 --> 00:16:19,780
Lord Li’s wife came again

268
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:21,180
to rush father

269
00:16:21,300 --> 00:16:22,500
to marry me to her son.

270
00:16:26,100 --> 00:16:26,940
Huirou,

271
00:16:29,980 --> 00:16:33,060
Li Wei’s mother is shallow

272
00:16:33,220 --> 00:16:34,220
and average-looking,

273
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:37,220
but Li Wei’s artistic talent

274
00:16:39,820 --> 00:16:40,900
is exceptional.

275
00:16:41,220 --> 00:16:42,260
I can tell

276
00:16:42,260 --> 00:16:43,780
he’s a real gentleman.

277
00:16:51,740 --> 00:16:52,540
Let’s...

278
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:53,980
Let’s change the subject.

279
00:16:54,940 --> 00:16:55,700
I don’t want to talk about him

280
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:56,900
when I don’t have to see him

281
00:16:57,100 --> 00:16:58,500
or his family.

282
00:17:01,260 --> 00:17:02,220
My point is

283
00:17:02,700 --> 00:17:03,820
my days in the palace

284
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:04,740
are numbered.

285
00:17:06,020 --> 00:17:08,260
I’m partly responsible

286
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:09,460
for the friction

287
00:17:09,460 --> 00:17:11,140
between you and father this time.

288
00:17:12,820 --> 00:17:14,500
If you don’t forgive him,

289
00:17:15,340 --> 00:17:16,620
I’ll leave

290
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:20,340
with guilt.

291
00:17:25,340 --> 00:17:26,140
These proposals

292
00:17:26,140 --> 00:17:27,460
are all criticizing Di Qing

293
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:29,860
that he took shelter in the Great Xiangguo Temple

294
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:32,820
while the Capital was flooded.

295
00:17:33,860 --> 00:17:36,020
Chief Di requests to leave the Capital to rest

296
00:17:37,060 --> 00:17:38,380
due to illness.

297
00:17:39,980 --> 00:17:42,780
Let Imperial Physicians check him first.

298
00:17:44,460 --> 00:17:45,100
Yes.

299
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:46,460
Greetings, Your Majesty.

300
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:49,140
Your Majesty, are you feeling better?

301
00:17:52,860 --> 00:17:53,620
Father!

302
00:18:07,340 --> 00:18:09,620
Father, Her Highness came

303
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:12,500
with no liquor or meat

304
00:18:12,820 --> 00:18:13,900
but sutras.

305
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:16,980
Are you going to let her in?

306
00:18:55,620 --> 00:18:56,460
Have a seat.

307
00:19:23,260 --> 00:19:24,380
Are you getting better?

308
00:20:02,140 --> 00:20:02,940
I...

309
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:10,980
I guess I knew

310
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:12,340
you were always kind,

311
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:16,100
tolerant and considerate,

312
00:20:18,420 --> 00:20:19,820
so every time

313
00:20:21,020 --> 00:20:22,580
I was in the worst mood,

314
00:20:23,780 --> 00:20:24,940
I’d dump all those nasty words

315
00:20:26,700 --> 00:20:27,700
on you.

316
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:28,460
No.

317
00:20:31,300 --> 00:20:32,660
Wh...what?

318
00:20:35,700 --> 00:20:37,260
It wasn’t because I was tolerant.

319
00:20:42,780 --> 00:20:44,060
You knew exactly

320
00:20:52,340 --> 00:20:53,860
how much I love you.

321
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:15,140
Huaiji,

322
00:22:17,020 --> 00:22:17,820
do you think

323
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:20,580
father loves Her Highness?

324
00:22:22,900 --> 00:22:23,980
He must care about them,

325
00:22:26,580 --> 00:22:29,860
mother, Her Highness.

326
00:22:33,620 --> 00:22:34,380
But

327
00:22:35,460 --> 00:22:36,940
how could they stand

328
00:22:38,020 --> 00:22:39,740
that father didn’t love them the most.

329
00:22:45,340 --> 00:22:46,300
The most or not,

330
00:22:46,860 --> 00:22:47,700
it’s hard to judge.

331
00:22:58,700 --> 00:22:59,660
When I heard

332
00:23:01,100 --> 00:23:04,260
Cao Ping promised to father repeatedly

333
00:23:04,660 --> 00:23:05,700
that he’d stop seeing me

334
00:23:07,020 --> 00:23:08,340
in order to

335
00:23:09,460 --> 00:23:10,820
protect his own family,

336
00:23:15,420 --> 00:23:16,260
I knew instantly

337
00:23:18,180 --> 00:23:19,220
that my love for him was gone.

338
00:23:23,420 --> 00:23:24,500
I understand him,

339
00:23:25,780 --> 00:23:26,740
pity him

340
00:23:28,420 --> 00:23:29,620
and care about him,

341
00:23:34,220 --> 00:23:35,580
but I can’t love a man

342
00:23:35,580 --> 00:23:37,260
who doesn’t love me wholeheartedly.

343
00:23:40,260 --> 00:23:41,100
That day,

344
00:23:42,180 --> 00:23:43,380
I lost the hope to live

345
00:23:45,620 --> 00:23:46,580
because I thought

346
00:23:48,220 --> 00:23:49,060
in this word,

347
00:23:51,580 --> 00:23:52,660
no one would

348
00:23:54,500 --> 00:23:55,660
never abandon me.

349
00:23:57,300 --> 00:23:58,060
No.

350
00:24:03,820 --> 00:24:06,620
But you came that day,

351
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:08,700
Huaiji.

352
00:24:10,380 --> 00:24:11,100
Then I realized

353
00:24:12,340 --> 00:24:15,540
there was still one person

354
00:24:16,660 --> 00:24:18,020
who’d always be there for me.

355
00:24:28,020 --> 00:24:28,620
I...

356
00:24:29,980 --> 00:24:31,060
I dare not...

357
00:24:33,140 --> 00:24:33,940
Huaiji,

358
00:24:35,500 --> 00:24:36,460
you’re good-looking

359
00:24:37,820 --> 00:24:38,700
and smart.

360
00:24:40,780 --> 00:24:41,820
Hadn’t you entered the palace,

361
00:24:43,180 --> 00:24:44,460
you would’ve passed the exam with flying colors.

362
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:47,260
Officials would’ve scrambled

363
00:24:48,900 --> 00:24:50,100
to marry their daughters to you.

364
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:54,620
And you would’ve become court scholar.

365
00:24:58,020 --> 00:24:59,740
I’m willing to be your shadow.

366
00:25:09,300 --> 00:25:11,540
It’s my honor to shadow you.

367
00:25:21,700 --> 00:25:22,460
Huaiji,

368
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:24,260
look.

369
00:25:25,700 --> 00:25:26,620
Where’s my shadow?

370
00:25:30,580 --> 00:25:32,220
Right under your feet, princess.

371
00:25:49,860 --> 00:25:50,700
Huaiji,

372
00:25:52,980 --> 00:25:54,220
you are in my heart.

373
00:26:10,380 --> 00:26:11,100
Your Majesty,

374
00:26:12,100 --> 00:26:13,660
Prime Minister Wen
and Prime Minister Fu want to know

375
00:26:14,020 --> 00:26:15,940
if Your Majesty feels well enough

376
00:26:16,140 --> 00:26:18,380
to meet officials at the Hall of Arch

377
00:26:18,460 --> 00:26:19,900
to reassure them.

378
00:26:24,540 --> 00:26:25,900
Tell Zongshi and Taotao

379
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:27,700
to come to the palace with Zhongzhen more often.

380
00:26:28,500 --> 00:26:30,540
They can stay for a few days.

381
00:26:32,180 --> 00:26:33,220
It’s quiet here.

382
00:26:34,020 --> 00:26:36,460
They can liven things up.

383
00:26:39,980 --> 00:26:41,260
This fish soup looks good.

384
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:58,380
Your Majesty, you have finally recovered!

385
00:27:11,100 --> 00:27:13,180
I’m easily fatigued.

386
00:27:14,340 --> 00:27:17,980
Report imperatives

387
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:20,340
that need to be discussed

388
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:22,340
in front of me first.

389
00:27:23,620 --> 00:27:26,060
= Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =

390
00:27:26,140 --> 00:27:28,300
= Ouyang Xiu, courtesy name Yongshu =

391
00:27:33,780 --> 00:27:34,660
Your Majesty,

392
00:27:36,180 --> 00:27:39,460
= Sima Guang, courtesy name Junshi =
a month ago, Chief Executive Di

393
00:27:39,580 --> 00:27:41,700
was condemned for disrespect to Buddha

394
00:27:42,180 --> 00:27:43,820
when residing in the temple because of the flood.

395
00:27:44,100 --> 00:27:45,620
The public found his conduct inappropriate, too.

396
00:27:46,580 --> 00:27:48,500
We went to visit him

397
00:27:48,860 --> 00:27:50,260
and tried to persuade him

398
00:27:50,820 --> 00:27:54,380
that the Capital isn’t the same as the army.

399
00:27:56,860 --> 00:27:57,660
Persuade him?

400
00:28:00,180 --> 00:28:02,620
You all visited him

401
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:04,580
and persuaded him?

402
00:28:11,380 --> 00:28:15,260
All of you are renowned scholars.

403
00:28:16,660 --> 00:28:17,940
I’m sure

404
00:28:18,580 --> 00:28:20,420
you’re good at persuasion.

405
00:28:21,380 --> 00:28:23,420
Everything in the world,

406
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:27,780
such as four seasons, circle of life,

407
00:28:28,420 --> 00:28:30,140
can be your analogies

408
00:28:31,060 --> 00:28:32,780
for mockery.

409
00:28:32,980 --> 00:28:35,220
I’ve been there.

410
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:42,580
How did your visit

411
00:28:43,420 --> 00:28:45,500
and persuasion go?

412
00:28:47,340 --> 00:28:50,780
Di Qing is too sick to recover soon.

413
00:28:52,300 --> 00:28:53,580
In my opinion...

414
00:28:54,060 --> 00:28:57,500
Apparently,

415
00:28:58,180 --> 00:28:59,740
he’s no longer able to work

416
00:29:00,820 --> 00:29:02,460
and should step down from his position.

417
00:29:04,460 --> 00:29:05,740
Your persuasion

418
00:29:06,580 --> 00:29:08,540
paid off eventually.

419
00:29:10,380 --> 00:29:13,300
Over a hundred years of military records

420
00:29:13,460 --> 00:29:14,620
are stored in the Privy Council.

421
00:29:15,980 --> 00:29:17,260
They’ll rot or get lost

422
00:29:17,620 --> 00:29:19,300
with time.

423
00:29:20,780 --> 00:29:23,140
We need an official who’s well aware of history

424
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:25,780
and foreign affairs

425
00:29:26,180 --> 00:29:28,580
to lead others to organize and compile them.

426
00:29:29,820 --> 00:29:32,100
Di Qing isn’t qualified for the job

427
00:29:32,620 --> 00:29:33,580
or healthy enough to serve.

428
00:29:34,820 --> 00:29:35,820
Appoint him

429
00:29:36,220 --> 00:29:39,260
Consultant of the Cabinet
and Ministry of Supervision

430
00:29:40,660 --> 00:29:42,460
to leave the city to govern Chenzhou.

431
00:29:44,580 --> 00:29:45,940
Transfer Han Qi back

432
00:29:46,460 --> 00:29:47,580
to the Privy Council

433
00:29:48,380 --> 00:29:51,900
for the organization of the records.

434
00:29:59,620 --> 00:30:01,700
Permission to speak, Your Majesty.

435
00:30:12,940 --> 00:30:13,740
Your Highness,

436
00:30:13,780 --> 00:30:15,060
a letter from Qiuhe.

437
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:25,180
= Ms. Xiu =

438
00:30:34,860 --> 00:30:36,340
Qiuhe gave birth to another girl.

439
00:30:38,140 --> 00:30:39,300
She’s blessed

440
00:30:39,620 --> 00:30:40,700
with three daughters.

441
00:30:41,540 --> 00:30:42,740
Although she has no son,

442
00:30:43,100 --> 00:30:45,060
her husband refuses to have any concubine.

443
00:30:47,020 --> 00:30:48,420
Qiuhe admired Your Highness

444
00:30:48,620 --> 00:30:49,900
and was willing to stay with you,

445
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:52,660
but you still let her leave.

446
00:30:54,220 --> 00:30:55,940
She offered to keep you company,

447
00:30:56,380 --> 00:30:57,700
yet you turned her down again.

448
00:30:59,780 --> 00:31:00,980
She’s lucky.

449
00:31:03,340 --> 00:31:04,380
Reading her letters is enough.

450
00:31:06,460 --> 00:31:08,420
Her husband is friends with Yan Jidao

451
00:31:08,420 --> 00:31:09,860
and Scholar Ouyang.

452
00:31:10,580 --> 00:31:11,620
It’s inappropriate for her

453
00:31:11,660 --> 00:31:12,740
to come to the inner courtyard too often.

454
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:17,020
But you have fewer and fewer people

455
00:31:17,500 --> 00:31:19,460
to talk to.

456
00:31:57,580 --> 00:31:59,060
His Majesty’s friends

457
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:01,460
are fewer and fewer.

458
00:32:02,780 --> 00:32:05,500
So are mine.

459
00:32:07,020 --> 00:32:07,980
He and I

460
00:32:09,380 --> 00:32:11,820
living in separate chambers

461
00:32:14,100 --> 00:32:16,900
yet growing old together

462
00:32:20,460 --> 00:32:21,860
is sort of a happy ending.

463
00:32:23,900 --> 00:32:27,820
You’re working as a corrector.

464
00:32:29,340 --> 00:32:30,180
Yes.

465
00:32:31,980 --> 00:32:34,620
I read your proposal over and over.

466
00:32:36,140 --> 00:32:39,660
Others used shooting stars and floods as excuses

467
00:32:39,980 --> 00:32:41,540
to urge me to select the Crown Prince,

468
00:32:42,660 --> 00:32:45,180
while you stated

469
00:32:46,180 --> 00:32:47,300
that being a filial emperor

470
00:32:47,820 --> 00:32:50,180
isn’t just about carrying on the family line

471
00:32:50,620 --> 00:32:53,500
but more about carrying on ancestors’ legacy

472
00:32:53,980 --> 00:32:55,620
and passing it down to future generations.

473
00:32:57,340 --> 00:33:00,140
Then you expanded it further with examples

474
00:33:00,820 --> 00:33:03,020
of previous dynasties and my father

475
00:33:04,340 --> 00:33:07,460
to advise me to select the Crown Prince.

476
00:33:12,100 --> 00:33:14,300
You’re young and low-ranking

477
00:33:15,340 --> 00:33:18,740
but your proposal is most objective

478
00:33:18,780 --> 00:33:19,860
and convincing.

479
00:33:20,020 --> 00:33:22,380
I like it.

480
00:33:25,020 --> 00:33:26,740
What’s Your Majesty’s decision?

481
00:33:29,420 --> 00:33:30,740
You’re erudite

482
00:33:31,620 --> 00:33:32,980
and excelled at writing.

483
00:33:33,540 --> 00:33:36,380
You can be a historiographer.

484
00:33:38,940 --> 00:33:40,500
Your Majesty, I...

485
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:42,580
Are you afraid I’ll die

486
00:33:43,660 --> 00:33:45,420
before the Crown Prince is settled?

487
00:34:05,260 --> 00:34:07,180
They all knelt.

488
00:34:09,100 --> 00:34:10,060
Then I left.

489
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:20,540
Have some.

490
00:34:39,300 --> 00:34:40,740
“Over the decades-long reign of Your Majesty,

491
00:34:40,740 --> 00:34:42,740
the vacancy of the Crown Prince

492
00:34:43,020 --> 00:34:44,380
unsettles the state.

493
00:34:45,220 --> 00:34:47,460
Ancestors’ great legacy

494
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:50,780
can’t be left unattended.

495
00:34:51,500 --> 00:34:54,180
Necessary measures must be taken

496
00:34:55,020 --> 00:34:57,700
to ensure eternal peace”.

497
00:35:00,420 --> 00:35:01,820
Sima Guang is right,

498
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:05,540
whose statement is in the national interest.

499
00:35:06,700 --> 00:35:09,380
He can be of more help to the state.

500
00:35:18,740 --> 00:35:20,060
If anything happens to me,

501
00:35:22,580 --> 00:35:24,020
Zongshi will be my successor.

502
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:43,140
“Scholar, Grand Master,

503
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:45,380
Minister of Personnel,

504
00:35:45,540 --> 00:35:48,580
Secretary, historiographer

505
00:35:49,220 --> 00:35:52,100
purple goldfish sachet honoree Ouyang

506
00:35:52,460 --> 00:35:55,540
is loyal, honest, capable and dedicated...”

507
00:35:58,420 --> 00:36:00,020
Mr. Yan sent you this

508
00:36:00,180 --> 00:36:02,420
from Nanjing

509
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:03,380
in 1027 A.D.

510
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:05,860
He said

511
00:36:06,420 --> 00:36:08,180
the exam to select officials

512
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:11,180
tests more of students’ literacy skills

513
00:36:11,860 --> 00:36:13,620
than argumentation on politics.

514
00:36:14,380 --> 00:36:17,060
Considering the purpose of the exam,

515
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:18,420
such arrangement is reversed.

516
00:36:20,180 --> 00:36:23,780
However, it’s still too soon

517
00:36:23,900 --> 00:36:25,580
to change the exam.

518
00:36:30,060 --> 00:36:31,460
So I’m going to

519
00:36:31,460 --> 00:36:33,620
change the education method first.

520
00:36:37,100 --> 00:36:38,060
That year,

521
00:36:38,540 --> 00:36:41,660
Mr. Yan invited Mr. Fan to teach at the academy

522
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:45,620
focusing on responsibility

523
00:36:46,220 --> 00:36:47,500
and application of knowledge.

524
00:36:48,140 --> 00:36:50,700
He combined current affairs with the textbook

525
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:52,220
to break it down to students.

526
00:36:57,700 --> 00:36:59,740
September, 1043 A.D.,

527
00:37:01,180 --> 00:37:04,060
Ten Reform Propositions.

528
00:37:05,180 --> 00:37:06,500
In terms of the exam,

529
00:37:07,220 --> 00:37:08,540
the core is shifted

530
00:37:09,300 --> 00:37:12,260
from literature to argumentation,

531
00:37:13,100 --> 00:37:14,620
thus upgrading the standard.

532
00:37:15,300 --> 00:37:17,180
But the long-lasting trend is hard to be changed.

533
00:37:18,420 --> 00:37:20,020
Shi Jie at the Directorate of Education

534
00:37:20,300 --> 00:37:21,740
was against the rhetoric

535
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:23,460
and parallel Xikun Style

536
00:37:23,700 --> 00:37:25,180
but promoted

537
00:37:25,300 --> 00:37:27,300
the obscure style among students

538
00:37:28,780 --> 00:37:31,540
which raised Ouyang Xiu and others’ concerns.

539
00:37:32,020 --> 00:37:34,620
If that’s the trend at the Directorate

540
00:37:34,900 --> 00:37:36,260
and favored by the chief examiner,

541
00:37:37,100 --> 00:37:39,780
then talents selected by the exam

542
00:37:40,020 --> 00:37:41,500
will be a bunch of nerds

543
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:45,020
who know nothing about real life.

544
00:37:46,460 --> 00:37:48,180
“Who cares about the masses

545
00:37:48,820 --> 00:37:50,700
is regarded as dutiful

546
00:37:51,060 --> 00:37:52,740
and devoted.

547
00:37:53,060 --> 00:37:55,140
Your achievements are remarkable.

548
00:37:55,540 --> 00:37:57,740
Your writing

549
00:37:57,740 --> 00:37:59,900
is elegant and graceful.

550
00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:02,940
I hereby appoint you Examiner

551
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:04,820
with the title.”

552
00:38:19,060 --> 00:38:23,140
= Master Scholar =

553
00:38:23,900 --> 00:38:25,620
When Mr. Yan was Examiner,

554
00:38:26,180 --> 00:38:28,140
he picked Ouyang Xiu, who failed the exam twice.

555
00:38:29,900 --> 00:38:32,140
Since then, Ouyang Xiu gradually introduced

556
00:38:33,180 --> 00:38:34,420
the plain style in writing

557
00:38:34,620 --> 00:38:36,660
to express actual thoughts

558
00:38:36,660 --> 00:38:37,900
into the Academy.

559
00:38:38,340 --> 00:38:41,900
Now, he’s become the new Examiner.

560
00:38:43,180 --> 00:38:45,940
I wonder how the court will

561
00:38:46,620 --> 00:38:48,060
be impacted.

562
00:38:51,300 --> 00:38:52,820
= Directorate of Education =

563
00:38:52,860 --> 00:38:57,140
= 1057 A.D. =

564
00:39:00,780 --> 00:39:02,500
= Su Zhe, courtesy name Ziyou =
=Su Shi, courtesy name Zizhan =

565
00:39:02,500 --> 00:39:03,980
Liu Ji was so self-conceit that day.

566
00:39:04,300 --> 00:39:05,580
In terms of writing in the obscure style,

567
00:39:06,060 --> 00:39:07,460
you’re as good as him if not better.

568
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:10,580
You can beat him with it and top the list.

569
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:12,380
He’ll be ashamed.

570
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:14,100
Writing in the obscure style

571
00:39:14,860 --> 00:39:16,540
only to beat him

572
00:39:17,380 --> 00:39:19,180
isn’t worth it.

573
00:39:20,460 --> 00:39:23,020
I mean to top the list.

574
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:25,900
Not interested, either.

575
00:39:28,620 --> 00:39:29,980
Then what are you interested in?

576
00:39:31,740 --> 00:39:33,820
His Majesty already issued the decree

577
00:39:33,820 --> 00:39:35,180
to remove the rhetoric.

578
00:39:35,380 --> 00:39:36,340
While such long-standing bombastic style

579
00:39:36,340 --> 00:39:37,540
hasn’t been eradicated,

580
00:39:38,020 --> 00:39:39,300
officials and scholars are embracing

581
00:39:39,300 --> 00:39:40,100
the hard-to-understand

582
00:39:40,100 --> 00:39:41,180
intricate and obscure style.

583
00:39:42,340 --> 00:39:44,260
So my goal is to wipe that all out.

584
00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:49,620
Aren’t you afraid you’ll fail the exam?

585
00:39:50,700 --> 00:39:51,540
If so, I’ll go home,

586
00:39:52,980 --> 00:39:55,020
read and write, teach children,

587
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:56,300
make liquor and roast meat

588
00:39:57,180 --> 00:39:58,460
for the rest of my life.

589
00:40:00,300 --> 00:40:03,500
The exam is about to begin!

590
00:40:04,500 --> 00:40:05,860
- Let’s go! - Let’s go!

591
00:40:20,060 --> 00:40:20,740
Good!

592
00:40:21,380 --> 00:40:23,260
Great! Brilliant!

593
00:40:25,420 --> 00:40:26,820
This is mind-blowing!

594
00:40:29,380 --> 00:40:30,620
He deserves

595
00:40:31,260 --> 00:40:32,140
to top others.

596
00:40:32,820 --> 00:40:33,860
Incredible!

597
00:40:35,500 --> 00:40:37,260
What kind of talent is it?

598
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:38,780
Let me continue.

599
00:40:40,140 --> 00:40:42,140
This seems to be written

600
00:40:42,140 --> 00:40:43,540
by your disciple Zeng Gong.

601
00:40:47,060 --> 00:40:48,780
If he becomes the first place,

602
00:40:51,180 --> 00:40:52,380
there will be criticisms.

603
00:40:53,820 --> 00:40:56,540
Zeng Gong’s style is similar to this.

604
00:40:56,540 --> 00:40:59,180
His essays aren’t bad

605
00:40:59,180 --> 00:41:00,180
but not as stunning

606
00:41:00,740 --> 00:41:02,260
as this piece.

607
00:41:02,420 --> 00:41:04,540
= Mei Yaochen, courtesy name Shengyu =

608
00:41:04,540 --> 00:41:06,300
If not him,

609
00:41:07,900 --> 00:41:09,700
who else could have such talent?

610
00:41:10,180 --> 00:41:10,820
Right.

611
00:41:11,020 --> 00:41:13,020
Such a capable student

612
00:41:13,500 --> 00:41:15,740
should have already made a name of himself

613
00:41:17,060 --> 00:41:18,300
but none of us have heard of

614
00:41:18,300 --> 00:41:19,140
this person.

615
00:41:19,540 --> 00:41:21,220
All exam papers are copied out

616
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:22,460
and made anonymous.

617
00:41:23,060 --> 00:41:24,300
Whether this is Zeng Gong’s essay or not,

618
00:41:24,380 --> 00:41:25,540
there’s no doubt

619
00:41:25,740 --> 00:41:27,780
that it’s the best of all.

620
00:41:28,180 --> 00:41:29,740
Are we going to turn a blind eye to real talent

621
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:31,420
to avoid being criticized?

622
00:41:31,900 --> 00:41:34,340
But this time, we eliminated all students

623
00:41:34,620 --> 00:41:37,540
who piled on literary allusions

624
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:39,860
and adopted the obscure style in writing.

625
00:41:40,100 --> 00:41:41,340
= Fan Zhen, courtesy name Jingren =
The result of the exam

626
00:41:41,740 --> 00:41:43,900
concerns many people’s career.

627
00:41:44,420 --> 00:41:45,700
We’ll be facing a storm.

628
00:41:46,980 --> 00:41:49,860
Complaints, speculations, attacks

629
00:41:50,140 --> 00:41:51,220
are already installed for us.

630
00:41:52,460 --> 00:41:55,100
To revolutionize

631
00:41:55,140 --> 00:41:56,700
the literary trend,

632
00:41:57,900 --> 00:41:59,540
and even

633
00:41:59,940 --> 00:42:01,500
the entire political environment,

634
00:42:01,900 --> 00:42:03,940
their career should be concerned.

635
00:42:04,780 --> 00:42:05,980
A storm at this moment

636
00:42:05,980 --> 00:42:06,900
isn’t bad at all,

637
00:42:07,260 --> 00:42:08,860
from which everyone will know

638
00:42:09,420 --> 00:42:10,420
that obscurity

639
00:42:10,620 --> 00:42:12,260
is no longer welcomed by the court.

640
00:42:12,540 --> 00:42:14,780
Simplicity and practicality

641
00:42:15,100 --> 00:42:17,380
are the new standards.

642
00:42:18,180 --> 00:42:20,140
I agree

643
00:42:20,380 --> 00:42:22,060
but that’s all the more reason

644
00:42:22,860 --> 00:42:24,820
to not give the ill-intentioned excuse

645
00:42:25,100 --> 00:42:26,220
to accuse you

646
00:42:26,980 --> 00:42:28,740
of nepotism

647
00:42:28,740 --> 00:42:29,660
or even cliquism.

648
00:42:30,220 --> 00:42:33,500
You crossed off all essays in the obscure style.

649
00:42:33,740 --> 00:42:36,100
If Zeng Gong comes out on top,

650
00:42:38,260 --> 00:42:39,700
won’t that be too obvious?

651
00:42:43,060 --> 00:42:44,700
People will talk.

652
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:49,500
Whoever this is

653
00:42:50,260 --> 00:42:52,820
will excel eventually.

654
00:42:52,980 --> 00:42:54,420
The result of this exam

655
00:42:55,620 --> 00:42:57,100
won’t bury his career.

656
00:42:58,540 --> 00:43:01,380
But if the accusation

657
00:43:01,980 --> 00:43:03,260
of cliquism is made,

658
00:43:04,780 --> 00:43:05,660
we won’t be able

659
00:43:06,460 --> 00:43:08,820
to realize our goal

660
00:43:09,340 --> 00:43:10,860
and talents we selected

661
00:43:11,540 --> 00:43:12,980
will be implicated, too.

662
00:43:21,820 --> 00:43:22,940
This essay

663
00:43:26,180 --> 00:43:27,740
deserves more

664
00:43:29,900 --> 00:43:31,140
than a second place!

